    "en": {
      "title": "Extension of application referral period for admission of students to first grade",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "For the year 2023, the Ministry of Education has again extended the dates for calling for applications for the admission of children to the first grade of schools.",
        "Considering the requests made by the parents to extend the last date for submitting applications for the first grade of 2023, the application submission period has been extended to 15.08.2022."
      ],
